ActBank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of ARMIN MARTENS of East St. Paul, Manitoba, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Bank of Canada to hold office, during good behaviour, for a term ending February 28, 2005, in the place of Walter Dubowec, whose term has expired.
